OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cweeks after 'shocking' stabbing
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a 40-year-old man died
OL,8,Fin hospital weeks after being stabbed
OL,9,Fin a "shocking" attack.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to Hale
OL,12,FLane in Failsworth at around 9:50pm on
OL,13,FFriday, 19 June, following reports of
OL,14,Fan altercation.
OL,16,FSteven Dossett was treated for stab
OL,17,Fwounds at the scene and rushed to
OL,18,Fhospital. Greater Manchester Police
OL,19,Fhave confirmed that he died from his
OL,20,Finjuries on Saturday, 4 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
