OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cweeks after 'shocking' stabbing
OL,6,FDetectives say they are continuing to
OL,7,Fpursue multiple lines of enquiry.
OL,9,FFive people - four men and one woman
OL,10,Faged between 17 and 45 - were
OL,11,Finitially arrested on suspicion of
OL,12,Fgrievous bodily harm and assault
OL,13,Foffences. They have since been
OL,14,Freleased on bail while investigations
OL,15,Fcontinue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
